577e = decode_Principal(p, len, (data)->principal, &l);
578if(e) goto fail;
579p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
580len = principal_oldlen - principal_datalen;
581}
582}
583len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
584}
585if(size) *size = ret;
586return 0;
587fail:
588free_Event(data);
589return e;
590}

642int ASN1CALL
643encode_HDBFlags(unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, const HDBFlags *data, size_t *size)
644{
645size_t ret HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE = 0;
646size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
647int i HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
648
649{
650unsigned char c = 0;
651int rest = 0;
652int bit_set = 0;
653if((data)->do_not_store) {
654c |= 1<<0;
655}
656if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
657if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
658*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
659if (!bit_set) {
660rest = 0;
661while(c) {
662if (c & 1) break;
663c = c >> 1;
664rest++;
665}
666bit_set = 1;
667}
668}
669c = 0;
670if((data)->require_pwchange) {
671c |= 1<<5;
672}
673if((data)->locked_out) {
674c |= 1<<6;
675}
676if((data)->allow_digest) {
677c |= 1<<7;
678}
679if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
680if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
681*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
682if (!bit_set) {
683rest = 0;
684while(c) {
685if (c & 1) break;
686c = c >> 1;
687rest++;
688}
689bit_set = 1;
690}
691}
692c = 0;
693if((data)->allow_kerberos4) {
694c |= 1<<0;
695}
696if((data)->trusted_for_delegation) {
697c |= 1<<1;
698}
699if((data)->immutable) {
700c |= 1<<2;
701}
702if((data)->user_to_user) {
703c |= 1<<3;
704}
705if((data)->ok_as_delegate) {
706c |= 1<<4;
707}
708if((data)->require_hwauth) {
709c |= 1<<5;
710}
711if((data)->change_pw) {
712c |= 1<<6;
713}
714if((data)->require_preauth) {
715c |= 1<<7;
716}
717if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
718if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
719*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
720if (!bit_set) {
721rest = 0;
722while(c) {
723if (c & 1) break;
724c = c >> 1;
725rest++;
726}
727bit_set = 1;
728}
729}
730c = 0;
731if((data)->invalid) {
732c |= 1<<0;
733}
734if((data)->client) {
735c |= 1<<1;
736}
737if((data)->server) {
738c |= 1<<2;
739}
740if((data)->postdate) {
741c |= 1<<3;
742}
743if((data)->renewable) {
744c |= 1<<4;
745}
746if((data)->proxiable) {
747c |= 1<<5;
748}
749if((data)->forwardable) {
750c |= 1<<6;
751}
752if((data)->initial) {
753c |= 1<<7;
754}
755if (c != 0 || bit_set) {
756if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
757*p-- = c; len--; ret++;
758if (!bit_set) {
759rest = 0;
760if(c) {
761while(c) {
762if (c & 1) break;
763c = c >> 1;
764rest++;
765}
766}
767}
768}
769if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERFLOW;
770*p-- = rest;
771len -= 1;
772ret += 1;
773}
774
775e = der_put_length_and_tag (p, len, ret, ASN1_C_UNIV, PRIM, UT_BitString, &l);
776if (e) return e;
777p -= l; len -= l; ret += l;
778
779*size = ret;
780return 0;
781}

783int ASN1CALL
784decode_HDBFlags(const unsigned char *p HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, size_t len HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE, HDBFlags *data, size_t *size)
785{
786size_t ret = 0;
787size_t l HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
788int e HEIMDAL_UNUSED_ATTRIBUTE;
789
790memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
791{
792size_t Top_datalen, Top_oldlen;
793Der_type Top_type;
794e = der_match_tag_and_length(p, len, ASN1_C_UNIV, &Top_type, UT_BitString, &Top_datalen, &l);
795if (e == 0 && Top_type != PRIM) { e = ASN1_BAD_ID; }
796if(e) goto fail;
797p += l; len -= l; ret += l;
798Top_oldlen = len;
799if (Top_datalen > len) { e = ASN1_OVERRUN; goto fail; }
800len = Top_datalen;
801if (len < 1) return ASN1_OVERRUN;
802p++; len--; ret++;
803do {
804if (len < 1) break;
805(data)->initial = (*p >> 7) & 1;
806(data)->forwardable = (*p >> 6) & 1;
807(data)->proxiable = (*p >> 5) & 1;
808(data)->renewable = (*p >> 4) & 1;
809(data)->postdate = (*p >> 3) & 1;
810(data)->server = (*p >> 2) & 1;
811(data)->client = (*p >> 1) & 1;
812(data)->invalid = (*p >> 0) & 1;
813p++; len--; ret++;
814if (len < 1) break;
815(data)->require_preauth = (*p >> 7) & 1;
816(data)->change_pw = (*p >> 6) & 1;
817(data)->require_hwauth = (*p >> 5) & 1;
818(data)->ok_as_delegate = (*p >> 4) & 1;
819(data)->user_to_user = (*p >> 3) & 1;
820(data)->immutable = (*p >> 2) & 1;
821(data)->trusted_for_delegation = (*p >> 1) & 1;
822(data)->allow_kerberos4 = (*p >> 0) & 1;
823p++; len--; ret++;
824if (len < 1) break;
825(data)->allow_digest = (*p >> 7) & 1;
826(data)->locked_out = (*p >> 6) & 1;
827(data)->require_pwchange = (*p >> 5) & 1;
828p++; len--; ret++;
829if (len < 1) break;
830(data)->do_not_store = (*p >> 0) & 1;
831} while(0);
832p += len; ret += len;
833len = Top_oldlen - Top_datalen;
834}
835if(size) *size = ret;
836return 0;
837fail:
838free_HDBFlags(data);
839return e;
840}

855if((data)->allow_digest) { ret += 3; break; }
856if((data)->allow_kerberos4) { ret += 2; break; }
857if((data)->trusted_for_delegation) { ret += 2; break; }
858if((data)->immutable) { ret += 2; break; }
859if((data)->user_to_user) { ret += 2; break; }
860if((data)->ok_as_delegate) { ret += 2; break; }

862if((data)->change_pw) { ret += 2; break; }
863if((data)->require_preauth) { ret += 2; break; }
864if((data)->invalid) { ret += 1; break; }
865if((data)->client) { ret += 1; break; }

867if((data)->postdate) { ret += 1; break; }
868if((data)->renewable) { ret += 1; break; }
869if((data)->proxiable) { ret += 1; break; }
870if((data)->forwardable) { ret += 1; break; }

3619
3620void ASN1CALL
3621free_HDB_extension(HDB_extension *data)
3622{
3623switch((&(data)->data)->element) {
3624case choice_HDB_extension_data_pkinit_acl:
3625free_HDB_Ext_PKINIT_acl(&(&(data)->data)->u.pkinit_acl);
3626break;
3627case choice_HDB_extension_data_pkinit_cert_hash:
3628free_HDB_Ext_PKINIT_hash(&(&(data)->data)->u.pkinit_cert_hash);
3629break;
3630case choice_HDB_extension_data_allowed_to_delegate_to:
3631free_HDB_Ext_Constrained_delegation_acl(&(&(data)->data)->u.allowed_to_delegate_to);
3632break;
3633case choice_HDB_extension_data_lm_owf:
3634free_HDB_Ext_Lan_Manager_OWF(&(&(data)->data)->u.lm_owf);
3635break;
3636case choice_HDB_extension_data_password:
3637free_HDB_Ext_Password(&(&(data)->data)->u.password);
3638break;
3639case choice_HDB_extension_data_aliases:
3640free_HDB_Ext_Aliases(&(&(data)->data)->u.aliases);
3641break;
3642case choice_HDB_extension_data_last_pw_change:
3643free_KerberosTime(&(&(data)->data)->u.last_pw_change);
3644break;
3645case choice_HDB_extension_data_pkinit_cert:
3646free_HDB_Ext_PKINIT_cert(&(&(data)->data)->u.pkinit_cert);
3647break;
3648case choice_HDB_extension_data_hist_keys:
3649free_HDB_Ext_KeySet(&(&(data)->data)->u.hist_keys);
3650break;
3651case choice_HDB_extension_data_hist_kvno_diff_clnt:
3652break;
3653case choice_HDB_extension_data_hist_kvno_diff_svc:
3654break;
3655case choice_HDB_extension_data_policy:
3656der_free_utf8string(&(&(data)->data)->u.policy);
3657break;
3658case choice_HDB_extension_data_principal_id:
3659break;
3660case choice_HDB_extension_data_asn1_ellipsis:
3661der_free_octet_string(&(&(data)->data)->u.asn1_ellipsis);
3662break;}
3663}
